MUTUAL FUNDS

Water Island Capital was a pioneer in offering event-driven strategies in a liquid alternative format. Mutual funds advised by Water Island Capital provide transparency, liquidity, and low investment minimums. Please click here to learn more.





HEDGE FUNDS

Information on hedge funds managed by Water Island Capital is available to qualified investors and financial professionals. Please contact us if you would like to learn more.





SEPARATE ACCOUNTS

Water Island Capital advises separately managed accounts following our event-driven investment strategies. Please contact us if you would like more information about a customized separate account solution.





Water Island Capital's event-driven expertise is accessible in a number of different formats depending on your needs.














