Company Overview
Water Island Capital, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund manager. The firm provides its services to investment companies. It manages separate client-focused equity and fixed income portfolios. The firm launches and manages equity and balanced mutual funds. It also manages hedge funds for its clients. The firm invests in the public equity markets and fixed income across the globe. It employs event driven investment strategies to create its equity portfolios. Water Island Capital, LLC was founded in 2000 and is based in New York City.


